title: RHONJ Gia & Joe/RHOC Stacks + Valentines!
itunes:title: RHONJ Gia & Joe/RHOC Stacks + Valentines!
description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of New Jersey, which featured Gia and Joe getting into it, plus Jen and Jackie bonding. Over on The Real Housewives of Orange County, the women finish their Cabo trip and have a troubling game night featuring toil*t paper and pl*ngers. Danny also touches on an emotional relationship issue ahead of Valentine's Day.
